cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.AI, cs.IR 

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with activity detection in videos using deep learning techniques. 
2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes a novel approach to learn latent super-events using a soft attention mechanism and temporal structure filters. 
3. cs.MM (Multimedia) is another possible category as the paper deals with analyzing and processing videos. 
4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper proposes a new approach to improve activity detection using deep learning. 
5. cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is also a possible category as the paper deals with analyzing and retrieving information from videos.
